course_description: Prerequisites: BIOS 500, BIOS 501 or BIOS 506 or permission of the instructor. How to select probability samples and analyze data using simple random sampling, stratified random sampling, cluster sampling and multistage sampling. The software package PC-SUDAAN is used for data analysis.
